    "However, traditional approaches lack efficiency in handling complex images with fine details, as provided in the weakness (Table 2).",
    "In recent years, deep learning-based automatic segmentation approaches have outperformed traditional methods in terms of performance.",
    "Two well-known DL-based segmentation approaches are Semantic Segmentation and Instance Segmentation.",
    "Semantic segmentation assigns a category label to each pixel in an image, dividing the image into mutually exclusive sets, with each set identifying a valuable region of the original image (Jafar et al., 2022).",
